title: MOA VE JESO

verses.1:
Moa ve Jeso dia mihevitra
Ny momba ny fiainako
Moa jereny ve isan'andro re
Izay l√†lan-kizorako.
verses.2:
Moa ve Jeso dia mandre tokoa
Ny feo fitarainako
Mba henony ve, ka valiany koa
'Zany antso sy sentom-po.
verses.3:
Moa ve Jeso dia manafaka
Raha mafy ny ady aty
Moa ampiny ve, ka vonjeny e!
'Zao ity olo-mahantra ity
verses.4:
Moa ve Jeso mahafantatra
Ilay ora farany
Moa akaiky ve, hamikirana
'Zao ny sandrim-pitiavany.

chorus:
He! Fantatro he fantatro!
Fa akaiky Jeso izao
Izy tena tia, anio doria
Akaiky Jeso izao.
